{
  "stem": "2316.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, when we got to--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To a DP camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And life began.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of the camp was Bindermichl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Austria-- Linz, city of Linz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were many, many refugees, and many people who escaped the concentration camps, and some people who escaped in the woods, or in hiding with Gentiles, and from all sorts and walks of lives, and from all cities and countries.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it became like a small, little, tiny Jewish community with-- with I don't know how many buildings, maybe 20, 25 buildings, and maybe four or five, six families lived in a little suite.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we shared our-- we stood in line, and the UNRRA gave us food, and clothing, and shelter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would stand in line every day in soup kitchens, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was like-- I don't know-- like everybody came from the dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like a celebration of life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was such-- of course, I was a youngster.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I found some kids my own age.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And believe it or not, we-- we had a social hall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had dances.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had music.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They gave us-- They started to teach us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "School.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the camp, temporarily, they had a little schoolhouse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had-- I went to a movie, I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- I've skipped so many things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "On the trip, we got injured.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We got hurt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We got broken bones and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But it was beginning like-- like the sun started to shine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and we started to pick our pieces up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And everybody became family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You didn't have to be an aunt, an uncle, a cousin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Everybody was family.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But there was a lot of sadness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We would take the bus to go to Linz.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
